{"tid":221141,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(抄到足)勁似AppleWatch,小米推運動手錶可用達30日","createTime":"2017-04-28T13:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T12:48:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31163aa554a260468226d1267ff417aefd2096d4","tid":221141,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/001-118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F001-118.jpg&h=d2d29a90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除智能手環外，小米生態鏈旗下的米家眾籌近年亦推出了不少其他類型產品，比如今日他們就帶來全新集資項目「唯樂 GPS 運動手錶 Hey 3S」，是一款功能尚算全面的運動型智能手錶，而且價格更相當便宜。不過在該產品推出之後，隨即又惹來抄襲 Apple 設計的風波。<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/003-58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2F003-58.jpg&h=8e752998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意米家推出的產品往往都不是出自小米之手，而今次這款唯樂 GPS 運動手錶 Hey 3S（以下簡稱 Hey 3S）則是由深圳市遠峰運動科技有限公司負責生產。至於外型方面採用方形錶面設計，尺寸為 46.21 x 35.66 x 11.15mm，重量亦只有 38g 非常輕巧，錶帶採用通窿設計可保持手腕乾爽舒適，並可輕易更換其他款式錶帶。Hey 3S 錶帶設有黑、紅及綠等顏色選擇，但細看之下大家應該會發現它與 Apple Watch Nike+ 非常相似&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撇除外觀不提，作為一款運動型智能手錶 Hey 3S 的功能亦頗為實用，當中內置的 GPS + GLONASS 雙星定位可提供更快速及準確定位，再配合九軸運動感應器及光學心跳感應器，可以記錄低行走及踩單車時的移動距離、速度及實時追蹤心跳率等，而連上智能電話後亦可接收通知、控制音樂播放、提醒日程及監測睡眠狀況等。Hey 3S 具備 50 米防水功能，更聲稱每次充滿電後最長可連續使用 30 日。Hey 3S 現正於米家上集資，每隻價格為 539 元人民幣（約 608 港元），並預定 5 月 20 日正式出貨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/28/xiaomi-hey-3s-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2Fxiaomi-hey-3s-smartwatch%2Flife-tech%2Fwatch-wireless-home%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZov9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=46da7ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/28/xiaomi-hey-3s-smartwatch/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/</a>"},{"pid":"44e765cac93ee4dfc763d47261333d9342734d29","tid":221141,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2965e2556dd4a11541ae8d3f84e339130046d9d9","tid":221141,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8d0999456de7d85490090f991b8c7404229ec2","tid":221141,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:57:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8376f0ec227937c55d4c145f746bee81d2b24155","tid":221141,"uid":55951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小米不嬲扮人再用勁低價賣出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賤種"},{"pid":"d147ff5bdcbf0ec504be9798caca918f2ec01213","tid":221141,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579e9e76cbaf11547ad75cc2c93fee6c106ad49b","tid":221141,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:57:57.000Z","msg":"奶共 cock 唔滿意咪打官司告9 小米囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c8e23abc7bc6e51d6019672b14edc8343846cc","tid":221141,"uid":22068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"出隻圓形好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca61645e4bf30c27ef80c2c80d841717085173c","tid":221141,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"舊登支機有咩發言？"}]}